data.description: Prime location, just minutes away from the vibrant heart of Downtown Bastrop. What truly sets this property apart is its remarkable over 380 feet of frontage along Highway 71. This strategic positioning not only ensures easy access to the conveniences of city life but also presents incredible potential for commercial use or development opportunities, making it an investor's dream. 4 bedroom and 2 bath home sitting on over 4 acres, stainless steel appliances and lots of windows to bring in brightness and natural lighting. An additional guest house with full kitchen, 1 bedroom and 1  bathroom. It's hard to find a property in a location like this. Come see it!
